    "Ela anota rapidamente os nossos pedidos e corre para a cozinha."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:194
translate portuguese welch8date_26f19da2:

    # sst "Izzy's a sweet girl."
    sst "A Izzy é uma miúda simpática."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:195
translate portuguese welch8date_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:196
translate portuguese welch8date_7288cc24:

    # sst "Super sexy too."
    sst "E super sexy também."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:197
translate portuguese welch8date_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "Sem dúvida."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:199
translate portuguese welch8date_650af916:

    # sst "So, [pcname], I wanted to talk to you about something."
    sst "Então, [pcname], queria falar contigo sobre uma coisa."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:200
translate portuguese welch8date_3e09ca60:

    # sst "I kind of have a crush on you."
    sst "Tenho uma espécie de paixão por ti."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:201
translate portuguese welch8date_65a7cfea:

    # sst "I think you're funny, you're cute, and I love how you actually care about social problems."
    sst "Acho-te engraçado, acho-te giro e adoro o facto de te preocupares realmente com os problemas sociais."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:202
translate portuguese welch8date_97bcec87:

    # sst "I was just wondering... do you like me too?"
    sst "Estava só a pensar... também gostas de mim?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:205
translate portuguese welch8date_51ff6f14:

    # sst "Oh, thank the gods, I was afraid I might have made a big mistake here."
    sst "Oh, graças aos deuses, estava com medo de ter cometido um grande erro."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:208
translate portuguese welch8date_1f998150:

    # sst "Oh okay. No problem then."
    sst "Ah, tudo bem. Então não há problema."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:210
translate portuguese welch8date_c63e8c62:

    # "Ms. Welch and I have a somewhat uncomfortable dinner, then I take her back to the school and drop her off near her car."
    "A Sra. Welch e eu temos um jantar um pouco desconfortável, depois levo-a de volta para a escola e deixo-a perto do carro dela."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:211
translate portuguese welch8date_070b1822:

    # "It's not a good idea to get involved with her any more than I already am."
    "Não é boa ideia envolver-me com ela mais do que já estou."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:216
translate portuguese welch8date_a7710f60:

    # sst "I'm really happy that you feel the same way."
    sst "Estou muito feliz por sentires o mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:217
translate portuguese welch8date_2103e901:

    # sst "I should tell you, I'm really bad at controlling my urges. And sometimes my urges get me into trouble."
    sst "Devo dizer-te que sou péssimo a controlar os meus impulsos. E, às vezes, os meus impulsos metem-me em sarilhos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:218
translate portuguese welch8date_27c38463:

    # sst "We need to wait until you graduate and you're not in my class before we pursue any kind of relationship, okay?"
    sst "Temos de esperar até te formares e já não estares na minha turma antes de prosseguirmos com qualquer tipo de relação, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:219
translate portuguese welch8date_4e669a5e:

    # sst "If anybody suspects that our relationship is anything more than friendly, I could lose my job."
    sst "Se alguém suspeitar que a nossa relação é mais do que amizade, posso perder o meu emprego."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:220
translate portuguese welch8date_e86f9bb1:

    # sst "I like you a lot, but I love my job and I don't want to lose it."
    sst "Gosto muito de ti, mas adoro o meu trabalho e não quero perdê-lo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:221
translate portuguese welch8date_34b44705:

    # pc "I understand."
    pc "Eu entendo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:223
translate portuguese welch8date_4a831597:

    # sst "If we can keep things calm and on the down-low for now though, after you graduate, maybe we could see where things go, okay?"
    sst "Mas se conseguirmos manter as coisas calmas e discretas por enquanto, depois de te formares, talvez possamos ver como as coisas evoluem, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:224
translate portuguese welch8date_6c48c73f:

    # pc "That sounds good Ms. Welch."
    pc "Parece-me bem, Sra. Welch."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:225
translate portuguese welch8date_5ff805f3:

    # sst "Please, outside of class, you can call me Nora, okay?"
    sst "Por favor, fora da aula, podes chamar-me Nora, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:226
translate portuguese welch8date_001845b4:

    # pc "Okay, Nora."
    pc "Está bem, Nora."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:229
translate portuguese welch8date_ea33992e:

    # "We chit-chat a little while we eat, just about school and politics. Nothing super interesting."
    "Conversamos um pouco enquanto comemos, apenas sobre a escola e política. Nada de muito interessante."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:230
translate portuguese welch8date_586b1732:

    # "Then, when we're done, I drive her back to her car at the school."
    "Depois, quando terminamos, levo-a de volta ao carro dela na escola."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:235
translate portuguese welch8date_e684ed1f:

    # sst "Bye, [pcname]. Thanks for hanging out with me tonight. I really enjoyed it."
    sst "Adeus, [pcname]. Obrigada por teres passado esta noite comigo. Gostei mesmo muito."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:236
translate portuguese welch8date_7ebf0e6b:

    # pc "Me too, Nora."
    pc "Eu também, Nora."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:237
translate portuguese welch8date_3daf6d31:

    # sst "Ooh, something about you saying my name kinda gets me hot."
    sst "Uau, há algo em ti a dizer o meu nome que me deixa excitada."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:238
translate portuguese welch8date_f13707ef:

    # sst "I wish I could invite you over to my house. I'd love to spend some more time with you. Hear you say my name some more."
    sst "Quem me dera poder convidar-te para ires a minha casa. Adoraria passar mais algum tempo contigo. Ouvir-te dizer o meu nome mais vezes."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:239
translate portuguese welch8date_0ef672f8:

    # sst "But I'll be good."
    sst "Mas vou portar-me bem."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:241
translate portuguese welch8date_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/welch_goodnight2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/welch_goodnight2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:242
translate portuguese welch8date_a53d3b6c:

    # sst "Good night, [pcname]."
    sst "Boa noite, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:243
translate portuguese welch8date_a629b7f0:

    # pc "Bye, Nora."
    pc "Adeus, Nora."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:247
translate portuguese welch8date_8f81c243:

    # "She gets out of the car and I watch her walk over to hers, get in, and drive away."
    "Ela sai do carro e eu vejo-a a caminhar até ao dela, a entrar e a afastar-se."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:249
translate portuguese welch8date_757b78b4:

    # "I have no idea how I'm going to hold off until graduation with her. She's so fucking hot. I just want her right now."
    "Não faço ideia de como vou aguentar até à formatura com ela. Ela é tão sensual. Só a quero agora mesmo."

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:250
translate portuguese welch8date_6f95dc85:

    # "After taking a few moments to just breathe, I drive off."
    "Depois de tirar alguns momentos apenas para respirar, arranco."

